<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Request Approved - Start Fundraising</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .credentials {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Congratulations! Your Request Has Been Approved</h2>
        <p>Dear @Model.UserName,</p>
        <p>We're excited to inform you that your request to start fundraising for your school has been approved! You can now begin adding your class/team members and start selling.</p>
        <p>To get started, please use the following credentials to log in to your account:</p>
        <div class="credentials">
            <p><strong>Username:</strong> @Model.Username</p>
            <p><strong>Password:</strong> @Model.Password</p>
        </div>
        <p>For security reasons, we recommend changing your password after your first login.</p>
        <a href="@Model.LoginUrl" class="button">Log In to Your Account</a>
        <p>Once you're logged in, you can:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Add your class/team members</li>
            <li>Set up your fundraising goals</li>
            <li>Start creating and managing your sales campaigns</li>
        </ul>
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance getting started, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing our platform for your school fundraising needs. We're looking forward to helping you achieve your fundraising goals!</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>@Model.Company Support Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>